--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

2.1 REPOSITORY ASSETS — PUBLIC USE LICENSE

    Subject to the terms of this License, you are granted a worldwide,
    royalty-free, non-exclusive license to:
    (a) use, reproduce, and distribute the Repository Assets;
    (b) use the Model Weights (yijing_v53_daoti.pt) for inference, including
        in commercial applications;
    (c) create derivative works based on inference.py;
    (d) publicly display and perform the Documentation;
    provided that:
    (i)   you retain all copyright, patent, trademark notices, and this
          License in all copies;
    (ii)  you clearly attribute 独立研究者，知白 as the original author;
    (iii) any derivative works of inference.py are distributed under
          this same License;
    (iv)  you do NOT reverse-engineer, decompile, or attempt to reconstruct
          the Architecture Source Code from the Model Weights or inference.py;
    (v)   you do NOT sublicense, resell, or redistribute the Model Weights
          (yijing_v53_daoti.pt) as a standalone product or as part of any
          model distribution platform, repository, or marketplace without
          prior written consent from 独立研究者，知白;
    (vi)  any derivative model created through fine-tuning of yijing_v53_daoti.pt
          shall also be distributed under this License.

    仓库资产 — 公共使用许可

    依据本许可证条款，您被授予全球范围内、免版税、非独占的许可：
    (a) 使用、复制和分发仓库资产；
    (b) 使用模型权重（yijing_v53_daoti.pt）进行推理，包括商业应用；
    (c) 基于 inference.py 创作衍生作品；
    (d) 公开展示和执行文档；
    但须满足以下条件：
    (i)   在所有副本中保留所有版权、专利、商标声明及本许可证；
    (ii)  明确标注原作者为 独立研究者，知白；
    (iii) inference.py 的衍生作品须依据本许可证分发；
    (iv)  不得从模型权重或 inference.py 中进行逆向工程、反编译或尝试重建
          架构源码；
    (v)   未经 独立研究者，知白 事先书面同意，不得将模型权重（yijing_v53_daoti.pt）
          作为独立产品或任何模型分发平台、仓库、市场的一部分进行转授权、转售或再分发；
    (vi)  任何基于 yijing_v53_daoti.pt 微调产生的衍生模型均须依据本许可证分发。

2.2 ARCHITECTURE SOURCE CODE — CASE-BY-CASE AUTHORIZATION

    Architecture Source Code is NOT included in the public repository.
    Architecture Source Code is protected as a trade secret.

    Access to Architecture Source Code (model class definitions, training
    scripts, loss functions, data processing pipelines) requires a separate
    written authorization from 独立研究者，知白.

    架构源码 — 逐案授权

    架构源码不包含在公开仓库中。
    架构源码作为商业秘密受到保护。

    获取架构源码（模型类定义、训练脚本、损失函数、数据处理流水线）需要
    独立研究者，知白 另行书面授权。

    To request access | 获取授权：

    (a) Academic institutions in the Chinese mainland (中国大陆学术机构):
        Submit an Academic Use Agreement including institution name, research
        scope, and responsible PI. Free of charge.
        提交学术使用协议，包含机构名称、研究范围和负责人。免费。

    (b) Commercial entities in the Chinese mainland (中国大陆商业实体):
        Submit a Commercial License Application. Terms negotiated per use case.
        提交商业许可申请。按使用场景谈判条款。

    (c) Entities outside the Chinese mainland (中国大陆境外实体):
        Submit a detailed proposal including use case, entity background,
        and compliance declaration. Reviewed case-by-case.
        提交详细方案，包含用途、实体背景和合规声明。逐案审核。


