    本许可证须遵守中华人民共和国所有适用的出口管制法律法规。

3.2 Architecture Source Code shall not be exported, re-exported, or transferred to:
    (a) any entity or individual subject to technology transfer restrictions
        under applicable Chinese law;
    (b) any military, intelligence, or surveillance organization;
    (c) any jurisdiction where such transfer is prohibited.

    架构源码不得出口、再出口或转让至：
    (a) 受适用中国法律技术转让限制的任何实体或个人；
    (b) 任何军事、情报或监控组织；
    (c) 禁止此类转让的任何司法管辖区。

3.3 Any person or entity receiving Architecture Source Code under a separate
    authorization may NOT further distribute, sublicense, or transfer the
    Architecture Source Code to any third party without explicit written consent
    from 独立研究者，知白.

    任何依据另行授权获得架构源码的个人或实体，未经 独立研究者，知白 明确书面同意，
    不得进一步分发、转授权或转让架构源码给任何第三方。


4. INTELLECTUAL PROPERTY | 知识产权
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

4.1 All title, ownership rights, and intellectual property rights in and to
    the DaoTi Foundation Model (Repository Assets, Documentation, Model
    Weights, and Architecture Source Code) shall remain with 独立研究者，知白.

    道体基础模型（仓库资产、文档、模型权重和架构源码）的全部所有权、产权和
    知识产权属于独立研究者，知白。

4.2 The DaoTi (道体) name, the TrigramSpace architecture, the Degenerate Ground
    State theory, and the HeLuo Ladder Network design are original intellectual
    property of 独立研究者，知白. This License does not grant any trademark
    rights.

    道体(DaoTi)名称、三爻空间(TrigramSpace)架构、退化基态理论以及河洛阶梯网络
    (HeLuo Ladder Network)设计是 独立研究者，知白 的原创知识产权。
    本许可证不授予任何商标权利。


5. PATENT NON-ASSERTION (FOR PUBLIC ASSETS ONLY) | 专利不主张（仅限公共资产）
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

