    agrees not to assert any patent claims against licensees for
    their use of the Repository Assets in accordance with this License, provided
    such use does not involve unauthorized access to Architecture Source Code.

    仅就仓库资产而言，独立研究者，知白 同意不对被许可方依据本许可证
